#Work area: ConsultingExpected travel: 0% - 80%Career status:Employment type: Regular Full TimeCOMPANY DESCRIPTIONSAP is the global market leader for business software and thus contributes a considerable part of the world's economic power grid. At SAP you get your chance to put your ideas into action with maximum impact.As an SAP HCM (Human Capital Management) Consultant, your charter is to personally maximise the value our clients receive from the application and effective implementation of SAP products and technologies through the delivery of professional services. As a market leader for business solutions, SAP offers you an ideal working environment for your professional and personal development.EXPECTATIONS AND TASKS-
Leading high quality implementation work in SAP HCM.-
Engage and contribute to consulting pre-sales like scoping studies, estimation, proposals.-
Guide and lead implementations from start to end - designing end to end processes, providing the right solutions and deliver on time and as agreed.-
Do quality gate audits at other implementations from time to time.-
Conduct continuous business improvement studies at SAP implementations.-
Initiate, participate and contribute to practice initiatives like knowledge management, services development, practice communication, certifications & white papers.WORK EXPERIENCE-
5+ years experience in SAP HR implementations, ideally in MENA.-
At least 3 end to end SAP HR implementations with 2 of them in lead capacity.-
Experience in building best-class teams & practices and nurturing talent is an added value.-
Advantage: Experience in the core HR topics of Personell Admin, Time Management, Organisational Management and Payroll. Strong in at least 3 of these SAP HCM topics:-
Talent Management Suite - PD, PMS, Skills, Talent Planning.-
New Age Technologies - Nakisa, HR Process & Forms, BOBJ - HR Analytics.-
Enterprise Compensation Management.-
eRecruiting.-
Travel Management.-
Employee Life Cycle Management - process experts.EDUCATION AND QUALIFICATION / SKILLS AND COMPETENCIES-
Graduate degree from reputed universities.-
Post graduation in HR would add value.-
Certified in SAP HCM.-
High on communication, presentation, customer interaction, team working and leadership skills.-
High on planning and execution - to be able to plan for projects and have the drive to execute and deliver as planned.-
Arabic speaker.
